com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang

Class RecycleBin<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.RecycleBin<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type parameter

    public abstract class RecycleBin<T>
extends Object
    This is a recycling mechanism to reuse short-term-lifecycle T objects of regular length. It is a convenience mechanism to optimize tight loops which would otherwise require careful and complex coding to minimize allocations and avoid excessive GC load
